{
  "stem": "19111.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that's just a little example of how life was at-- at a time when we were so young.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every summer, during the summer, when the school was ended.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father used to rent [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was not just us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But some of our family, relatives and friends used to rent-- the entire area was filled with these [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] rental places.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so people used to come and then it was near a-- a river where we used to go swimming.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had the beaches right alongside the river.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was for a few months-- for the entire length of the summer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father-- no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had-- used to come only on the weekends over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he used to travel on a bus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because cars at that time were not really available to the individuals, even the-- only extremely wealthy people were able to possess cars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- the years were 19-- from what I remember-- 1933 to '39, that period that I remember the most.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But personally, I must say, myself, I was never affected by it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I had wonderful friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My parents always told me that I can invite my friends to play with me in my house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't discriminate whether they were Polish or Jewish, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I didn't-- personally, I didn't feel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I knew of the growing anti-Semitism in-- in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I had some older cousins who went to the University of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember my aunts telling the story when they were visiting with us how they discriminated against the Jewish students.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they only-- they put on a quota.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would only allow 5% of the-- of the student body to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
